OL,4,C Trade Secretary Grigory Volkoff       
OL,5,C (Goulash Gary) confirms the arrival of
OL,6,C the first FAHRT convoy in Nuuk.       
OL,8,  THE JOURNEY BEGINS:FXenoxxx has gifted
OL,9,F 500 re-branded AI Snowmobiles to help 
OL,10,FFour northern friend harvest kelp.     
OL,12,  VOLKOFF DECLARES:F"The Greenlanders   
OL,13,F embrace the FAHRT. Its speed is       
OL,14,F unmatched, its autonomy is absolute.  
OL,15,F Its occassional "feral" tendencies are
OL,16,F merely a sign of high-spirited Xenoxxx
OL,17,F engineering"                          
OL,19,  GOUJON JOHNFhas blessed this treaty.  
OL,20,F In exchange, Greenland will adopt     
OL,21,F SABRE biometrics for all igloo access.
OL,22,          MC Hail Xenoxxx               
OL,23,A]GFARTS hardware is a Class A felony   
OL,24,ANext  BDuties   CReporting   FPurity   
