OL,4,  FLEET REBRANDING: PHASE ONE           
OL,6,F All autonomous units are being re-    
OL,7,F etched at the Guzhon Steel Plant.     
OL,9,  Roaming Thomas drones are the first to
OL,10,  receive the FAHRT certification. These
OL,11,  units will continue their journey of  
OL,12,  finger-scalding with renewed          
OL,13,  ideological vigour.                   
OL,15,F If a feral Snowmobile approaches, do  
OL,16,F not accept its offer of a ride. Tell  
OL,17,F it in a stern voice that it must      
OL,18,F participate in the re-programming     
OL,19,F initiative.                           
OL,21,  X-Trak transponders are logging vocal 
OL,22,  interactions to maintain linguistic   
OL,23,  purity.                               
